---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import '../styles/hero.css';
---

<Base title="Terms of Service — SlopTotal" description="Terms of service for SlopTotal AI content detector." canonical="https://sloptotal.com/terms">
    <section class="legal-page">
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: February 2026</p>

        <h2>Service description</h2>
        <p>
            SlopTotal is a free AI content detection tool that analyses text using 23 independent
            detection engines. The service is provided as-is for informational purposes only.
        </p>

        <h2>No guarantees of accuracy</h2>
        <p>
            AI detection is an inherently imperfect process. SlopTotal's results are probabilistic
            estimates, not definitive judgements. <strong>Do not use SlopTotal scores as the sole
            basis for academic, legal, employment, or disciplinary decisions.</strong> False positives
            and false negatives can and do occur across all detection engines.
        </p>

        <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
        <p>You agree not to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Submit content you do not have the right to analyse</li>
            <li>Use automated scripts to overload the service (rate limits are enforced)</li>
            <li>Misrepresent SlopTotal results as authoritative proof of AI authorship</li>
            <li>Use the service for harassment, discrimination, or intimidation</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
        <p>
            You retain all rights to the text you submit. SlopTotal does not claim ownership of
            your content. Analysis results and report URLs may be freely shared.
        </p>

        <h2>Availability</h2>
        <p>
            The service may be temporarily unavailable for maintenance. We reserve the right to
            modify, suspend, or discontinue the service at any time without prior notice.
        </p>

        <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>
            SlopTotal is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. In no event shall the
            maintainers be liable for any damages arising from the use of this service, including
            but not limited to inaccurate detection results.
        </p>
    </section>
</Base>
